@node screenmodes.aaa "AAA Screenmodes 0.121"
@toc aaa

    - AAA Screenmodes -

        - Chunky Pixel Modes in 2, 4, 8, 16 BITs

        - Hybrid Chunky Pixel Modes in combinations of Chunky Pixel Modes

        - 800x560x9 using DRAM

        - 800x560x24 using VRAM hybrid modes

        - 1280x1024x24 using VRAM and multiple sets of AAA chips

