    - AAA Hardware Stats -

        - 4 VLSI integrated chips

        - DRAM and VRAM support

        - 40 DMA channels with dynamic allocation

        - 32 BIT Blitter

        - 32 BIT Copper

        - chunky pixel modes, hybrid chunky pixel modes

